<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hopeful" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hopeful,</orth> 1) full of hope, of expectation of good fortune: <emph>the world's h. expectation,</emph> Ven. Ded. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 5.4.35" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 35</bibl> <cit><quote>the h. mother,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 1.2.24" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 2, 24</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) exciting good hopes, likely to obtain or ensure success: <bibl n="shak. mm 1.1.60" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. I, 1, 60</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 2.3.85" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 3, 85</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 3.2.41" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 41</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.1.97" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 1, 97</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.2.126" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 2, 126</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.420" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 2, 420</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 2.3.49" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 3, 49</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 1.2.15" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 2, 15</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>